      "span_text": "The NF-kB consensus oligonucleotides (sense: AGTTGAGGGGACTTTCCCAGGC; antisense: GCCT-GGGAAAGTCCCCTCAACT) labeled with P by T4 polynucleokinase (Promega, Madison, WI) were incubated with nuclear extracts in binding buffer (10 mM Tris pH 7.6, 1 mM DTT, 0.5 mM EDTA, 2 mg polydI-dC and 10% Glycerol) at 30uC for 30 minutes."
